// outward from a central connected body. Near c=(0.35, −0.05) the set
// is connected with three primary arms decorated by fine plume structures.
// Derivative: 3z²·der / (1+|z|²) for normal-map shading (approximation).
// Supports normal-map shading (colorScheme 50-63).
